citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - Access and inspection of records and property: A responsible adult shall be made available to
accompany APHIS officials during the inspection process.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1330 on
10/27/2015.
I called the licensee at 1330 and left a message. I waited for 30 minutes and did not receive a call back. No one
came home while I was there.
End of report.
